data.description:
A stunning 3-bedroom 3.5 3.5-bath townhouse nestled in a peaceful and highly sought-after community. Upon stepping inside, you'll immediately notice the spaciousness and inviting atmosphere this home exudes. With 3 generously sized bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, there's no shortage of comfort and convenience here. The primary bedroom features ample closet space and an en-suite bathroom. Picture yourself enjoying your morning coffee or unwinding after work on the balcony just off the kitchen. The open kitchen design seamlessly flows into the family room, making it an ideal layout for entertaining friends and family. Whether you're hosting a lively gathering or simply enjoying a cozy night in, this space provides endless possibilities for creating cherished memories. Looking for additional flexibility? The terrace level offers a versatile bedroom or flex space along with another full bathroom, allowing you to customize the area to suit your unique needs. This extra living space could be transformed into a home office, guest suite, or even a dedicated recreation area. A Washer and dryer hook up located upstairs and a spacious 2 car garage. Conveniently located just 1.5 miles from Smyrna Market Village, close to Braves Stadium, Belmont Village, and major interstates, ensuring easy access to various amenities and easy access to an array of dining, shopping, and entertainment options. Commuting is a breeze for those working in town. This is a non-smoking home. Call about pets.
